Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:09.57,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1\blur3}You need to show me babe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:17.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}So, I’m not just a doll you manipulate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Remember, it’s my role and I play it well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.54,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}You’re giving me attention
